so i dont get it how if u int you can get banned even if its in a norms game
however; someone can go 2/12 or 0/10 in a RANKED game but say &quot;sorry guys im just bad&quot; but get away with it; its not their fault that they lack some skill but you cant flame them either due to banning system
it feels as if the banning system is just there to support bad players while it is used against good players e.g. when someone flames a feeder &quot;im gonna report you for toxicity but i can 100% get away with wasting 40 mins of ur time because &quot;im bad&quot;
